00:13:23.690 --> 00:13:26.041 align:middle line:84%
And you had a very
shiny looking life.

00:13:26.041 --> 00:13:26.740 align:middle line:90%
Right.

00:13:26.740 --> 00:13:30.880 align:middle line:84%
Well because you know what--
-- this is what I discovered

00:13:30.880 --> 00:13:32.380 align:middle line:84%
