00:13:32.380 --> 00:13:34.640 align:middle line:84%
when you've been
abused you get really

00:13:34.640 --> 00:13:36.560 align:middle line:90%
good at being a chameleon.

00:13:36.560 --> 00:13:39.160 align:middle line:84%
You get really good at
being what the people

00:13:39.160 --> 00:13:41.110 align:middle line:90%
