00:13:41.110 --> 00:13:42.760 align:middle line:90%
So what they drink, you drink.

00:13:42.760 --> 00:13:43.890 align:middle line:90%
If they smoke, you smoke.

00:13:43.890 --> 00:13:45.920 align:middle line:84%
If they like this,
you like this.

00:13:45.920 --> 00:13:51.760 align:middle line:84%
And so I really
became a chameleon.

00:13:51.760 --> 00:13:53.270 align:middle line:84%
But the thing is
is that the essence

00:13:53.270 --> 00:13:56.030 align:middle line:84%
of who I am, the
authenticity of who I am,

00:13:56.030 --> 00:13:57.560 align:middle line:90%
