00:14:01.080 --> 00:14:04.560 align:middle line:84%
Because this isn't the
person that I connected with.

00:14:04.560 --> 00:14:06.670 align:middle line:84%
This isn't the person
that I engaged with.

00:14:06.670 --> 00:14:08.180 align:middle line:90%
Where is she?

00:14:08.180 --> 00:14:10.400 align:middle line:84%
And then I couldn't
push it back down.

00:14:10.400 --> 00:14:12.300 align:middle line:84%
And so there would
be this conflict,

00:14:12.300 --> 00:14:14.850 align:middle line:90%
internal and external.

00:14:14.850 --> 00:14:15.800 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:14:15.800 --> 00:14:18.540 align:middle line:84%
And then I would assume that
in this-- what you're saying

00:14:18.540 --> 00:14:21.570 align:middle line:84%
is not only were you a
chameleon but a part of you

00:14:21.570 --> 00:14:23.470 align:middle line:90%
