00:14:23.470 --> 00:14:25.440 align:middle line:90%
Completely.

00:14:25.440 --> 00:14:27.280 align:middle line:90%
Do anything to have love.

00:14:27.280 --> 00:14:29.860 align:middle line:84%
Do anything so that
people won't leave you.

00:14:29.860 --> 00:14:32.320 align:middle line:84%
Do anything so
that you don't have

00:14:32.320 --> 00:14:34.060 align:middle line:84%
to be alone to
deal with this pain

00:14:34.060 --> 00:14:37.890 align:middle line:90%
that is coursing through you.

00:14:37.890 --> 00:14:38.790 align:middle line:90%
That's a big one.

00:14:38.790 --> 00:14:41.370 align:middle line:84%
And now as I'm listening
to you on this,

00:14:41.370 --> 00:14:44.120 align:middle line:84%
