how vulnerable little children

00:14:58.220 --> 00:14:59.390 align:middle line:90%
are to their environment.

00:14:59.390 --> 00:15:02.180 align:middle line:84%
To do the things you say and
do to them that our parents

00:15:02.180 --> 00:15:03.080 align:middle line:90%
