00:18:24.330 --> 00:18:26.250 align:middle line:90%
back into the same patterns.

00:18:26.250 --> 00:18:27.190 align:middle line:90%
Well, yeah.

00:18:27.190 --> 00:18:29.940 align:middle line:84%
But you know the older you
get, the more sophisticated

00:18:29.940 --> 00:18:31.590 align:middle line:90%
you get at it.

00:18:31.590 --> 00:18:32.860 align:middle line:90%
So what's that mean?

00:18:32.860 --> 00:18:37.060 align:middle line:84%
Well, it means that you
learn to cover up those things

00:18:37.060 --> 00:18:39.960 align:middle line:90%
that you perceive as flaws.

00:18:39.960 --> 00:18:44.310 align:middle line:90%
And I learned what not to say.

00:18:44.310 --> 00:18:46.640 align:middle line:84%
How to act with certain
groups of people.

00:18:46.640 --> 00:18:47.580 align:middle line:90%
How to show up.

00:18:47.580 --> 00:18:48.340 align:middle line:90%
How to dress.

00:18:48.340 --> 00:18:51.760 align:middle line:90%
How to bring my talents in.

00:18:51.760 --> 00:18:55.590 align:middle line:84%
But not to show them
what I was feeling.

00:18:55.590 --> 00:19:00.280 align:middle line:84%
Not to talk about the pain
