00:19:00.280 --> 00:19:06.250 align:middle line:84%
And to suppress my own voice
if it meant in any way, shape,

00:19:06.250 --> 00:19:09.440 align:middle line:90%
or form, there was danger.

00:19:09.440 --> 00:19:13.510 align:middle line:84%
And when I hear you say that, I
